Yesterday it was the third and last day for faithful> and pilgrims> to greet and honor &nbsp; Pope Francis>, who died on 21 April.&nbsp;From the morning of Wednesday 23 April at 11 am until 8 am this morning more than 150,000 people went to St. Peter's Basilica. The Basilica was opened until 2:30 a.m. to reopen this morning at 5:40 &nbsp; to cope with the great audience. &nbsp;
<h2>Trump landed at Fiumicino</h2>
