<div </div
&nbsp;
<h2> Extraordinary closures for the Conclave
The Sistine Chapel will be closed to the public on Monday, April 28, "for the needs of the Conclave," the Holy See announced. "All visits to the Vatican Gardens and the Necropolis of the Via Triumphalis> are also suspended."
&nbsp;
